parameters:
Taro, still unable to recover from his breakup with Luna,
remained an empty shell even as nearly a year had passed.

\N<Taro>Sigh... It's been "10 months" since I came back... I just
can't find the motivation to do anything... No reason to
try, which I guess is to be expected...

\N<Taro>Luna-chan is gone... I know that, but I can't stop dwelling
on it... Me.
\N<Taro>Sigh... I'm hungry, maybe I should go buy something...
\N<Taro>...A package? But I haven't ordered anything online...
\N<Taro>A device...? I don't remember ordering this...

\N<Taro>There's some video on it... Is it an ad? I'm really not in
the mood to watch it now...

\N<Taro>What's this uneasy feeling... Well, I might as well check it
out...
